{
  "stem": "1062.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There is a name for it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A rolling pin.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A rolling pin, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Put it on a rolling pin and bring it over to the-- to the oven.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was known as a [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the guy by the oven, he was known as a shiber.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he would take it and throw it into the oven.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He make-- I would say that from the time you take the-- the-- the flour to the time the matzah comes out, maybe-- maybe it was 14, 15 minutes, the whole-- the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was a community undertaking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I want you to know that this used to take weeks, weeks to go with the wheat.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It-- but it was a project.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a big project.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It wasn't like today, you go into a Waldbaum's, and you say, give me 3 pounds of whatever-- you know, matzahs.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There, you-- you-- you worked for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you appreciated it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And after-- all right, this was Passover, mostly Passover.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Also, Passover was the holiday where if somebody got a new suit or a new pair of shoes or whatever, it was for Passover.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was the time when-- when-- when the kids used to get new clothes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] During the High Holy Days-- Shovuos, for example.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "After Passover comes Shovuos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now Shovuos is that holiday when-- when-- when Jews are reminded that they received the Torah.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In every house, they used to go out and tear off branches from walnut trees because the walnut tree is in bloom.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it has a very good smell.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they would put in the house full of branches with walnut trees.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
